'''Christian Chamber of Commerce and Industry''' is an organisation of [[christian]] businesspeople in [[India]]. It was set up in 2010 to act as platform for Christian businesspeople so that they may benefit from networking and achieving a higher rate of growth. Its headquarters is in [[Hyderabad]] [[India]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ccciindia.in/Default.aspx |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203033334/http://ccciindia.in/Default.aspx |archivedate=2014-02-03 |df= }}</ref>

